habitat_description: This species inhabits northern reaches of Semidesert Grassland, and scattered patches in Madrean Evergreen Woodland (Brennan and Holycross 2009). .Also in Arizona, it can be found in the Pajarito, Baboquivari, Santa Rita, and Huachuca mountains. In New Mexico, Peloncillo Mountains. Also found in northeastern Chihuahua south through western slopes of Sierra Madre Occidental of Chihuahua, Sonora, Durango, Sinaloa, Nayarit, Jalisco, and Zacatecas; coastal plain of central Sinaloa south through Nayarit (Degenhardt et al. 1996; Stebbins 2003).
